		<p><strong>To log out, completely exit your Web browser when you are finished.</strong></p>
		<ul>
			<li><em>Windows users:</em> Close all Web browser windows.</li>
			<li><em>Mac users:</em> Quit your Web browser.</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Otherwise, your NetBadge access will last for 9 hours if you're on Grounds (1 hour if you're off
